data.description: Fantastic 3bd/2ba in the highly desirable neighborhood of Ashbury Park across the street from Herald Elementary.  With a perfect blend of functionality and style this home features a Large Living Area with Vaulted Ceilings.  Kitchen has Beautiful Wood Grain Cabinets, Travertine Tile, Granite Countertops with Black Appliances. Breakfast bar and Dining Area.  Split floor plan.  Backyard overlooks Stocked Neighborhood Pond perfect for Sunday afternoon fishing.  This home features tons of Comfort and Convenience close to shopping, schools, parks and highways for easy commuting. Storm Shelter in Garage.  Neighborhood has Splash Pad.  This home is located in an area that will qualify for a USDA loan.
